This is an app created to demo some of Simple XML capabilities with CSS and JS Extension and Custom Visualizations.
Data used is mostly cooked up or coming from Splunk's _internal index for demo purpose only.

default/data/ui/
    nav
        default.xml - App Navigation to show only four dashboards and give theme color for App.
    views
        overall_health.xml - Heatmap and Service Tree view for Entity and Service with drilldown to open Threshold chart.
        health_comparison.xml - Dashboard using Simple XML Chart with Multiseries and CSS Overrode for series compare in Legend.
        service_flow.xml - Dashboard with Simple XML CSS extension for Image Overlay with data icon and color.
        advanced_view.xml - Advanced dashboard with Simple XML CSS and JS for creating modal with chart and table.
    panels
        pp_SplunkNavBarTabView.xml - Pre-Built panel for CSS override for Dashboard Menu to appear as Tabs (should be moved to dashboard.css)
appserver/static/
    scripts
        advanced_model.js - Required JS file for Simple XML JS extension with SplunkJS code.
        table_with_tooltip.js -  Required JS for Table Heatmap tooltip and Table Tile Icon switch.
    imges
        svg
            online_shopping_design.svg - SVG background image for Glass Table Dashboard for Image Overlay.
            conf20-nav-logo.svg - SVG logo for Splunk conf20.
        png
            dashboard-background.png - PNG background image for image overlay example.

Dependencies:
    Status Indicator Custom Viz - Used for Font-Awesome Icons - https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/3119/
    Region Chart viz - Drilldown chart with thresholds - https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/4911/
    Network Diagram Viz - For plotting Service dependency - https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/4438/
